      "author": "CharlotteK (Charlotte Kirkham)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hey Aysha! Just to confirm; you are looking for a way to always have the Map View as an available board view?</p>\n<p>If so, you can click the plus sign + icon next to your “Main table” and then “More views” and you can add the Map View there:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/3/3c62da1136649b955644e127a2eeca541561a422.png\" title=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-17 at 1.57.58 PM\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/3/3c62da1136649b955644e127a2eeca541561a422_2_682x500.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-17 at 1.57.58 PM\" width=\"682\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">Screen Shot 2023-01-17 at 1.57.58 PM</span><span class=\"informations\">1564×1146 84 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/b/b62494a84ac108af6f6ab58f64b80989d4d28565.png\" title=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-17 at 1.58.39 PM\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/b/b62494a84ac108af6f6ab58f64b80989d4d28565_2_601x500.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-17 at 1.58.39 PM\" width=\"601\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">Screen Shot 2023-01-17 at 1.58.39 PM</span><span class=\"informations\">1364×1134 98.7 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/a/ad786751f4f7635c5c390aea62558c3a60111818.png\" title=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-17 at 1.59.19 PM\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/a/ad786751f4f7635c5c390aea62558c3a60111818_2_690x383.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-17 at 1.59.19 PM\" width=\"690\" height=\"383\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">Screen Shot 2023-01-17 at 1.59.19 PM</span><span class=\"informations\">2544×1414 359 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><